            "title": "紐約聯儲研究發現關稅九成負擔由美企承擔 哈塞特稱相關人員應受處分",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"紐約聯儲研究發現關稅九成負擔由美企承擔 哈塞特稱相關人員應受處分\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/96JsuUBElnNfTyvhbRyYyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/d86c6ea0-0d47-11f1-9fff-02a4ab704afd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">紐約聯儲研究發現關稅九成負擔由美企承擔 哈塞特稱相關人員應受處分</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
