        {
            "title": "金馬年淘金尋找下一個熱門族群 分析師：創新板小而美具潛力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tgDWzT3_ohKZbSe0vK0.jw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/dc6ade84a108d4482d5fcb672b9cd2d4\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%87%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%B9%B4%E6%B7%98%E9%87%91%E5%B0%8B%E6%89%BE%E4%B8%8B-%E5%80%8B%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80%E6%97%8F%E7%BE%A4-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB-%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%BF%E5%B0%8F%E8%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%B7%E6%BD%9B%E5%8A%9B-011003711.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-19 09:59:17",
